{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>What is Njuma?</strong></h2><br><strong>Njuma</strong> is a narrative driven pixel art game with an offbeat interpretation of the Game Jam\u2019s theme: <strong>Take a Deep Breath.</strong><br><br>Draw your last breath and become the family's Spirit-Guide and <strong>Guardian of the Ancestral Tree</strong>. Help your descendents in their final moments by bringing them comfort and serenity as they transition to the afterlife.<br><br>The Ancestral Tree withers, generational trauma lurking in its shadow. You must piece together a tragedy and soothe a soul-scar which refuses to heal. The Fate of the family is in your hands.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>What you can expect</strong></h2><br>A short walking simulator game, where you interact and get help from items and NPC's in the environment to interpret the story.<br><br>The NPC's interact with you as you walk close to objects, giving you clues of what they are seeking.<br><br>Pick up items, and place them to make a choice. Your choice matters!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>About development</strong></h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2743320/extras/credits_ella_01.png?t=1706256792\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2743320/extras/credits_ben_01.png?t=1706256792\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2743320/extras/credits_embla_01.png?t=1706256792\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2743320/extras/credits_emmy_01.png?t=1706256792\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2743320/extras/credits_joe_01.png?t=1706256792\" /><br><br>This game was developed as a submission for the Lv. 99 Game Jam in 2023. It was developed in the span of 10 days, and worked on further fo